{"word":"Hanani","slug":"hanani","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hanani</b> <a href=\"#/H2607\">H2607</a> <br/> 1. Son of Heman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=4'>1Ch 25:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=25'>1Ch 25:25</a><br/> 2. A prophet who rebuked Asa, king of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=7'>2Ch 16:7</a><br/> 3. Father of Jehu the prophet<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=1'>1Ki 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=7'>1Ki 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=2'>2Ch 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=34'>2Ch 20:34</a> <br/> - Possibly identical with a prophet who rebuked Asa above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=7'>2Ch 16:7</a> <br/> 4. A priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=20'>Ezr 10:20</a><br/> 5. A brother of Nehemiah and keeper of the gates of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=1&verse=2'>Neh 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=2'>Neh 7:2</a><br/> 6. A priest and musician<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=36'>Neh 12:36</a>"}]}